# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UltraTable Frontend — Environment Variables (Vite)
# These apply to /apps/web and /apps/admin.
# Copy this file to .env in the project root.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── API Target ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# URL of the backend service. Vite dev server proxies /graphql
# and /api to this target. Default: http://127.0.0.1:8080
# In production (Vercel), the frontends call the service directly.
# VITE_API_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:8080
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.ultratable.io

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NOTE: Service-side environment variables (DATABASE_URL, etc.)
# are documented in apps/service/.env.example
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
